headline: Does Cencora’s Strong 42% Rally Signal More Growth Ahead in 2025?
summary: If you’re standing at a crossroads, wondering what to do with Cencora stock, you’re not alone. With shares closing recently at $318.00 and quietly notching up a 42.6% gain over the past year, there’s a real sense of momentum. The stock outperformed in the last five years too, leaping an astonishing 244.5%. That’s a growth story that’s caught more than a few eyes.
